**Examining aria-selected use**

I’m considering whether the `aria-selected` attribute should be a boolean instead of a string. React does support "Booleanish" strings, but it seems that using `aria-selected={false}` would be a more accurate approach. It feels important to put this patch in place to ensure clean coding practices. I really want to provide the best, most reliable guidance on this, so making sure about the correct data type matters a lot!
